@node Main "DoorMaze - Documentation"

                             'DoorMaze'  1.0

                           by Charles-N. Jacob

  'DoorMaze' is a @{" Workbench game " link play} in which you have to find the
exit of a 99 by 99 spaces area where you only see a 5 by 5 spaces
area at a time. To move about, you have to open 'doors',
represented by horizontal and vertical bars that are located next
to your position. Sometimes, these doors are replaced by brick
walls and you must move around them.

  To complicate matters a little, the exit, located somewhere at
the edge of the game area, is surrounded by colored doors. One of
these doors has to be opened with a corresponding coloured key that
has to be found somwhere in the game area.

  Complete the game in the least amount of moves.

  Have fun!

